WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.940
So another tool we've also seen on 'Around the Versa' is Data Forge,

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:05.690
which is quite difficult to explain.

00:00:05.750 --> 00:00:08.900
Within the game, almost everything you see has lots of configuration data.

00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:12.550
So one of the great benefits of Data Forge, it allows us to have master records

00:00:12.550 --> 00:00:14.460
and then variant records.

00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:16.710
And this means we save a lot of time updating records,

00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:19.470
and configuring these items that appear in the game.

